---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Kuzupost PhotoStrips - Privacy Policy">
    <div
        class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex flex-col items-center py-16 px-4 md:px-6 overflow-hidden bg-neo-white"
    >
        <!-- Background accents -->
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none"
            style="background-image: radial-gradient(#111827 2px, transparent 2px); background-size: 30px 30px; opacity: 0.1;"
        >
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-4xl flex flex-col items-center">
            <h1
                class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase text-neo-black bg-neo-cyan inline-block px-6 py-3 border-4 border-neo-black shadow-[8px_8px_0_0_#111827] transform -rotate-1 mb-8 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform cursor-pointer text-center"
            >
                <i class="fa fa-shield-halved mr-3"></i>PRIVACY POLICY
            </h1>

            <div
                class="w-full bg-neo-white border-4 border-neo-black p-6 md:p-8 shadow-[8px_8px_0_0_#111827] space-y-6 relative"
            >
                <!-- Decorative element -->
                <div
                    class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 w-16 h-16 bg-neo-pink border-4 border-neo-black transform rotate-12"
                >
                </div>

                <div
                    class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-neo-black font-bold font-mono"
                >
                    <p
                        class="text-2xl font-black bg-neo-yellow p-4 border-4 border-neo-black shadow-[4px_4px_0_0_#111827] mb-8 transform -rotate-1"
                    >
                        Privasi Anda adalah nomor satu (setelah hasil foto yang
                        bagus, tentu saja).
                    </p>

                    <h2
                        class="text-3xl font-black uppercase border-b-4 border-neo-black pb-2 inline-block mb-4 mt-8"
                    >
                        1. Pengumpulan Data
                    </h2>
                    <p
                        class="leading-relaxed bg-black/5 p-4 border-l-[8px] border-neo-cyan"
                    >
                        Kuzupost PhotoStrips beroperasi sepenuhnya di browser
                        Anda. Kami <strong>tidak</strong> menyimpan gambar atau video
                        Anda di server kami. Semua pemrosesan filter dan penggabungan
                        strip foto dilakukan secara lokal di perangkat Anda.
                    </p>

                    <h2
                        class="text-3xl font-black uppercase border-b-4 border-neo-black pb-2 inline-block mb-4 mt-8"
                    >
                        2. Penggunaan Kamera
                    </h2>
                    <p
                        class="leading-relaxed bg-black/5 p-4 border-l-[8px] border-neo-pink"
                    >
                        Aplikasi ini memerlukan akses ke kamera perangkat Anda
                        (webcam) semata-mata untuk tujuan mengambil foto secara
                        real-time yang akan dirangkai menjadi photo strip.
                        Aliran video tidak pernah dikirimkan atau dipantau oleh
                        kami.
                    </p>

                    <h2
                        class="text-3xl font-black uppercase border-b-4 border-neo-black pb-2 inline-block mb-4 mt-8"
                    >
                        3. Penyimpanan Lokal
                    </h2>
                    <p
                        class="leading-relaxed bg-black/5 p-4 border-l-[8px] border-neo-yellow"
                    >
                        Kami mungkin menggunakan Penyimpanan Lokal (Local
                        Storage) browser Anda secara eksklusif untuk menjaga
                        urutan sesi foto Anda dari halaman bilik utama (Photo
                        Booth) ke halaman Editor. Data ini dihapus saat sesi
                        selesai atau cache browser dibersihkan.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-12 flex justify-start">
                    <button
                        onclick="window.history.back();"
                        class="inline-block bg-neo-black text-neo-white font-black text-lg py-3 px-6 border-4 border-neo-white shadow-[4px_4px_0_0_#111827] hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0_0_#111827] hover:-translate-y-1 active:shadow-none active:translate-y-2 transition-all uppercase tracking-widest"
                    >
                        <i class="fa fa-arrow-left mr-2"></i> KEMBALI
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
